{"tid":1201184,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［非理性討論］其實勇武抗爭係想達到咩目標","createTime":"2019-06-11T03:13:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T04:54:20.000Z","uid":186989,"like":8,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"849f1314521db992cc6f49b8e5a54fd482035613","tid":1201184,"uid":186989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T03:13:34.000Z","msg":"睇咗幾個連登post，都係叫人有組織咁衝擊政總/立法會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但真心想問衝擊/包圍有咩用？想達到咩目的？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n姑勿論衝擊警方防線實會受傷，捉到實俾人告。雨傘嗰時話衝，成效 = 0，又俾政府同班唔中意暴力既市民有話柄。而且個目標唔係應該針對建制同個政權咩？成個連登啲人都勁仇視警察，咪on9正中班建制下懷，班官擺明係推班警察出嚟擋你地，連登仔就on99眼都紅晒話要用燃燒彈又剩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />班警察都係執行職務啫，佢地都有家庭架，都係香港市民一部分<br />\n<br />\n話想阻止立法包圍/佔領立法會，其實只係個場地問題，根本政府都未驚過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咪遲啲再開會囉，反正政府坐定粒6數夠票<br />\n<br />\n最有效既方法係咪應該直送認清會投支持票既立法會議員，係佢地辦事處門口死纏爛打叫口號又好，同佢討論又好，疲勞轟炸到佢地覺得煩，只少都唔會咁順利話投票就啦投啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個政府同議會擺到明不公義，但勇武係咪真係有用呢？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歡迎罵戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b83e8387b5b47bc7a51488e1821adc48a5119b0","tid":1201184,"uid":138233,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T03:32:41.000Z","msg":"如果你可以直接同議員打到招呼咪ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n問題係無得選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aad8504205a36f388a0114383de96c12ca867b14","tid":1201184,"uid":60545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T03:34:47.000Z","msg":"你覺得自己可以見到民健聯啲狗？<br />\n經秘道去都可以啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85059c526f931de1ea666fbb50728c3c23b4e90b","tid":1201184,"uid":32906,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T03:35:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔同你嘈，各有各做。</span>"},{"pid":"241da2c6bde1c860b794385cf286e7db060bf8d0","tid":1201184,"uid":28435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T03:36:10.000Z","msg":"靠你感化建制派 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8876ddcb7699be7210f5677384f0ad31b0bbe63","tid":1201184,"uid":186989,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"8b83e8387b5b47bc7a51488e1821adc48a5119b0","tid":1201184,"uid":138233,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T03:32:41.000Z","msg":"如果你可以直接同議員打到招呼咪ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n問題係無得選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T04:05:25.000Z","msg":"但政府一日夠票，一日都可以繼續推個法案架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />怕你班勇武有牙咩"},{"pid":"e1e65f84cf4cc64e40a5c27502c517ea957e362c","tid":1201184,"uid":157994,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T04:07:27.000Z","msg":"其實警察都係自己人，佢地都係想香港好<br />\n我地唔好再內鬥啦"},{"pid":"56d6eeb0c11078767eafb323d52b6ce89643eac8","tid":1201184,"uid":186989,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T04:22:22.000Z","msg":"我覺得大部分連登仔（包括我自己）有perception bias（認知偏見），主觀地認為好多人撐勇武，但其實真實世界係咪真係咁多人會參與衝擊，咁多人撐勇武抗爭？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有幾百人係時事台時版話點組織點支援，已經足夠會令到連登睇落絕大多數都係撐勇武。但返工睇下呢個社會身邊既人，真係投入支持勇武既有幾多個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be5415abb63fccf993672b2517dae668ad86f8d4","tid":1201184,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"849f1314521db992cc6f49b8e5a54fd482035613","tid":1201184,"uid":186989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T03:13:34.000Z","msg":"睇咗幾個連登post，都係叫人有組織咁衝擊政總/立法會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"h